{"tid":407970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞回應獨立公投：支持多數加泰人意願","createTime":"2017-09-21T00:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T07:31:46.000Z","uid":36494,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d08f987d2e5ba8b46e57d16bf1e4369fa440beb","tid":407970,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:16:55.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區計劃於下月一日舉行獨立公投，而中央政府則認為公投違法，周二更突撃搜查加泰多個政府部門，拘捕當地多名官員。球會巴塞隆拿周三發公開信回應事件，譴責任何阻礙民主、自主以及言論自由的行為。公開信又寫道，巴塞隆拿會以文明、和平、理想的方式，繼續支持大多數加泰人民的意願。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，巴塞官方於6月曾公開支持《全民公投協議》(Pacto Nacional por el Refer&eacute;ndum），而該協議旨在取得組織或個人的聯署，以支持加泰隆尼亞舉行獨立公投。"},{"pid":"973469ef7f77296a538400416f646dd81d7e0ed4","tid":407970,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"以後無西甲打毗了"},{"pid":"0faea8f50e344fc311f6f2a60052e6b875084cd0","tid":407970,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後無西甲打毗了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n皇馬變到拜仁咁 山寨王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1c646b8b95850fb94d1366f4553e3b0a18b951","tid":407970,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"美斯可以去法甲sm屁馬"},{"pid":"95207218957b2690fc28fb8a5c5fb60b3d7da7c3","tid":407970,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"d291308ab8dac26b738554b6f5ac9c4d27c5cbb4","tid":407970,"uid":123320,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"體育唔關政治事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我淨係想睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d9c115c18e0a64d035111d7698174aff9bd4d9","tid":407970,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"點解人地可以成個加泰地區都咁團結<img s